6.1 xhit =2 and yhit =2¶

6.1.1. x-y相邻：¶

  • 2.1x-y $\pm$ 30
  • Single-hit: 425, 440 / x-y
  • Double-hit:411,417,418 / x2e[0] = x2e[1] and y2e[0] = y2e[1]
